      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal mapping between simulation input parameters and experimental conditions must demonstrate equivalency within specified tolerances for all validation test cases.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters between simulation and experiment not formally assessed. Boundary condition values assumed equivalent to experimental conditions without documented verification of measurement-to-model parameter mapping."
